CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 18, 1941, page 4 reads: "The Tech Ice Cream Co., treated Bill Bojangles Robinson last Tuesday morning to a 50- pound Eskimo Pie, which is Bojangles favorite dessert. Bill doesn't drink and is moderate in his habits. From all appearances he is enjoying the idea! The presentation was broadcast by radio station WWSW with the announcer shown on the right.--Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Bill "Bojangles" Robinson pretending to bite large Eskimo Pie ice cream bar, standing with WWSW radio station announcer, possibly Joe Tucker, near microphone
